elements.title: Mary Creighton Bailey
elements.contents: ... that teacher Mary Creighton Bailey was awarded the Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany for her services in the improvement of education in Germany shortly after World War II?

elements.title: a winter storm in December 2017
